name_pretty: Google Cloud Airflow Service V1 API
ruby-cloud-description: google-cloud-airflow-service-v1 is the official client library for the Google Cloud Airflow Service V1 API. Note that google-cloud-airflow-service-v1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-airflow-service instead. See the readme for more details.
